<div class="layout-collapsible-section" id="cs8522761609">
    <h3 class="layout-collapsible-section__headline">
        <span class="layout-collapsible-section__headline-inner">Akne Kid Joe</span>
        <span class="layout-collapsible-section__headline-more layout-collapsible-section__headline-more--collapsed">mehr</span>
        <span class="layout-collapsible-section__headline-less layout-collapsible-section__headline-less--collapsed">schliessen</span>
    </h3>
    <div class="layout-collapsible-section__body layout-collapsible-section__body--collapsed">
        <div class="layout">
<div class="layout-text">
    <div class="page" title="Page 1">
<div class="section">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p>AKNE KID JOE sind der picklige kleine Scheißer aus der ersten Reihe und allergisch auf voll viel, v.a. auf „Summer of 69“ von Bryan Adams.</p>
<p>Mukke zwischen dilettantischem Schrammelpunk, NDW und Classic-Rock. Textlich zwischen Kartoffelstampfer, Shitstorm und Traumabewältigung.</p>
<p>And after all, they ́re your wonderwall.</p>
</div>
<p><a href="https://aknekidjoe.com">aknekidjoe.com</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
